bibtex.dom
Class BibtexFile

java.lang.Object
  bibtex.dom.BibtexNode
      bibtex.dom.BibtexFile
public final class BibtexFile
extends BibtexNode

This is the root of a bibtex DOM tree and the factory for any bibtex model - the only way to create nodes. For an example, check out the documentation for the constructor of BibtexNode.
